tables.table_schema: CREATE TABLE data_science_data (id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), age INT, occupation VARCHAR(50))

CREATE TABLE data_analysis (
    analysis_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    analysis_name VARCHAR(50),
    user_id INT,
    data_source_id INT,
    analysis_date DATE,
    FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES users(user_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (data_source_id) REFERENCES data_sources(data_source_id)
);

CREATE TABLE predictions (
    prediction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    project_id INT,
    model_id INT,
    prediction_value VARCHAR(255),
    FOREIGN KEY (project_id) REFERENCES projects(project_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (model_id) REFERENCES models(model_id)
);
CREATE TABLE data_science.projects (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), description TEXT, created_at TIMESTAMP)
